# Engineer-track artifacts from the agentic scheme discovery pipeline.
#
# When an admin approves a candidate in /admin/discovery, the route handler
# serialises the SchemeCandidate to a YAML manifest in this directory. The
# filename pattern is `<scheme_id-or-uuid8>-<YYYY-MM-DD>-<short_hash>.yaml`.
#
# Manifests are the canonical reference for the engineer who updates the
# Pydantic rule module in backend/app/rules/ (or hand-codes a new rule when
# the candidate has no matching scheme_id).
#
# This directory is intentionally tracked so the layout exists on a fresh
# clone; the manifests themselves are deliberately gitignored so reviewer
# triage activity does not bloat the repo.
